</p><p>A discrete example is a finite <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w=
iki/Cyclic_group" title=3D"Cyclic group">cyclic group</a> of order <i>n</i>=
. Convolution operators are here represented by <a href=3D"https://en.wikip=
