analog of the convolution theorem continues to hold, along with many other =
aspects of <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Harmonic_analysis" titl=
e=3D"Harmonic analysis">harmonic analysis</a> that depend on the Fourier tr=
ansform.
</p>
