?title=3DConvolution-superposition_algorithm&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;redlink=
=3D1" class=3D"new" title=3D"Convolution-superposition algorithm (page does=
 not exist)">convolution-superposition algorithm</a>.<sup class=3D"noprint =
